N2  - In this note, we redefine and reinterpret Cord's risk constraint that will be used in selecting the optimal portfolio of investment projects. A sensitivity analysis is carried out via derivation of efficient sets of portfolios for different levels of investment. Also the theoretical foundations of the model are discussed.
